{"tid":1873921,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix 公告《生化危機》真人劇集故事內容","createTime":"2020-02-11T02:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-29T21:45:07.000Z","uid":1886,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4d34cce9b359731e6d603c0637cdf172d8b719bf","tid":1873921,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:24:27.000Z","msg":"由 CAPCOM 出品的知名遊戲《Resident Evil》(生化危機)，在去年推出《Resident Evil 2》重新在全球牽起一陣熱潮，Netflix 更宣佈將為《Resident Evil》製造亦推出一連八集的真人劇集。在昨日，有網民就發現 Netflix 在網站上公布了劇集中的改編劇情，讓一眾粉絲先睹為快。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/02/10/resident-evil-netflix-series-details-leak-online/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F02%2F10%2Fresident-evil-netflix-series-details-leak-online%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=u5wkwi0qRaq%2FdbVqa5yG4VpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=fb00b637\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/02/10/resident-evil-netflix-series-details-leak-online/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"c18501487b16a942738ead54132f602141fcdb29","tid":1873921,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:25:24.000Z","msg":"有網民在昨日發現 Netflix 在官方網站上發佈了一段《Resident Evil》劇集的劇情，當中講到「Clearfield 小鎮長期以來一直身處於保護傘公司、已經廢棄的 Greenwood Asylum 以及華盛頓特區三大陰影之下。一直到了今天，即發現 T 病毒的 26 年後，上述三者的最大秘密將會被一一揭露出來。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/2-11.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F02%2F2-11.png&h=35ce6e69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據外媒的報道，《Resident Evil》將會在今年 6 月正式開拍，並預期會在南非進行取景，最快有望可以在明年上半年推出第一季。"},{"pid":"2e18d32b447980c21fd114c0612ccc5f2b131bb8","tid":1873921,"uid":57543,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-11T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"武漢實地拍攝？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=